### Create price book
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pricing/price-books
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: local-create-price-book

{
  "code": "PB-DEFAULT",
  "name": "Default Price Book",
  "currency": "MYR",
  "validFrom": "2026-01-01"
}

### List price books
GET http://localhost:8080/api/pricing/price-books
X-Correlation-Id: local-list-price-books

### Create price rule
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pricing/rules
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: local-create-price-rule

{
  "priceBookId": "{{priceBookId}}",
  "ruleCode": "FD-500G-BASE",
  "description": "Base price for frozen dumplings",
  "skuId": "{{skuId}}",
  "minQuantity": 0,
  "unitPrice": 12.50,
  "priority": 10,
  "validFrom": "2026-01-01"
}

### List price rules
GET http://localhost:8080/api/pricing/rules
X-Correlation-Id: local-list-price-rules

### Quote price
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pricing/quote
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: local-price-quote

{
  "retailerId": "{{retailerId}}",
  "deliveryZone": "NORTH",
  "items": [
    {
      "skuId": "{{skuId}}",
      "quantity": 3.000
    }
  ]
}
